  "texts": [
    "We used this dataset because it is large, comprehensive, and publicly available.",
    "It is roughly the same size as the commonly used WikiSQL dataset, which is one of the largest annotated text to SQL datasets.",
    "Unlike WikiSQL, it provides the create statements for each table to limit hallucinations, which is a practice that is achievable in a production application.",
    "This dataset is not specific to marketing, and the conclusions generated from this study should generalize to any application involving SQL query generation, assuming the tables are somewhat similar to those in the dataset (e.g.",
    "they don't have thousands of columns)."
  ],
